{"tid":642584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（集氣）同女朋友復合","createTime":"2018-04-26T01:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T18:59:05.000Z","uid":77132,"like":36,"dislike":174,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8bd95f9faac2b5d60e6b71d0f54845acec0ec6","tid":642584,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:36:48.000Z","msg":"同女朋友近呢個月情況急轉直下，我又唔太體諒佢我比太少空間佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我自己知衰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,唔好咁對我啦我知道自己有時候情緒太激動，我保證下次唔會再咁，直到失去既時候先知道你有幾重要即使未來既唔知會點但係，我只係知道現在唔追返你就會後悔一世，我從未試過對一個人咁愛<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日我唔會搵你先，想你諗清楚但係我唔信我地感情咁脆弱，我地經歷好多，我明白到冇左你我就好似一個小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日冇搵，我好擔心你成日瞓到唔知醒<br />\n成日同你講叉電你就講充電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專登激我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食剩啲野冇人幫你執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家快啲屌撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老婆對唔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過2日睇戲希望復合到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我愛你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n祝各位巴打早日出pool全家身體健康<br />\n<br />\n幫手集氣<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/093620_ab90a516208428904e6cda435f0e305b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F093620_ab90a516208428904e6cda435f0e305b.png&h=a3961bce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbecb3c24f9a68a2756060101b946bacba0b4b77","tid":642584,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:37:48.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b5652c57b399eb43ee544ba597a8daad3b6127","tid":642584,"uid":3510,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"咁即係老婆定女朋友？"},{"pid":"e2b0e34047ba517a0ddf964277815d7e39594494","tid":642584,"uid":77132,"like":1,"dislike":90,"score":-89,"quote":{"pid":"d1b5652c57b399eb43ee544ba597a8daad3b6127","tid":642584,"uid":3510,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"咁即係老婆定女朋友？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:39:50.000Z","msg":"我已經當佢老婆<br />\n我願意將所有野比佢<br />\n佢係一個好女仔黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833bd54cecb2e2a96e4184ef83d0fc3ecaeefa45","tid":642584,"uid":63432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"同路人<br />\n真心想改過唔係一頭半個月就改到"},{"pid":"458456124f040e410ceb416dac83308597d73496","tid":642584,"uid":110002,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"冇左女朋友就成個小朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你都要從自己身上着下手，改變下<br />\n<br />\nAnyway 加油"},{"pid":"df516f4a90dcfa4ce5d42f74c8f73abc3b1bdfe2","tid":642584,"uid":77132,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"833bd54cecb2e2a96e4184ef83d0fc3ecaeefa45","tid":642584,"uid":63432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"同路人<br />\n真心想改過唔係一頭半個月就改到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:42:33.000Z","ms